4","tid":1847053,"uid":110108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T08:05:48.000Z","msg":"推，封關呀柒婆"},{"pid":"0fc66631edaf84b501b5f0648d1de3912d748a06","tid":1847053,"uid":149181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T09:18:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1a8173367212afc8f74f1f64cc3bdc49d607b2e1","tid":1847053,"uid":13387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T09:19:31.000Z","msg":"留名一推"},{"pid":"3f457ffdba9f062d178a3a355762e33634b004b1","tid":1847053,"uid":13387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T09:21:42.000Z","msg":"柒婆都係唔肯封福田 羅湖口岸<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔罷工一齊中肺炎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"091863dd5915a2c437e3fb8a02e07c2067b7fb81","tid":1847053,"uid":278201,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7d98a61009c5d7c07bdfccf65ab537590a6a6e60","tid":1847053,"uid":149181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T00:53:13.000Z","msg":"醫院前線既醫護當然重要危急<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但係我想講老人院既情況都好值得留意，因為到呢刻係好撚多老人院係未<span style=\"color: red;\">封院</span>大撚把大陸西家屬落黎探病，又冇感染控制可言，仲要大把老人院既PCA都係大陸人，個個新年都係大陸番落黎再番工好撚危險<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同埋我想講呢排天氣唔穩定，大把廢老入院，出出入入好易惹到番老人院<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />醫院爆發仲可以勉強控制到，但如果老人院爆發呢個生化疾病係講緊會好易<span style=\"color: red;\">社區爆發</span> 到時係會控制唔到<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以大家經過老人院都要小心<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />上街或去老院探病戴番口罩（唔好同我講話焗，棺材仲焗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />） 同埋幫手推下，一定要比更多人知道老人院既情況<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 老人院既護士都係醫護黎架<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔可以割！！<br />\n<br />\n利申：有幫手番part time ,岩岩先聽到有個大陸西PCA宜家係大陸番落黎準備晏就番工，仆街腦細乜撚措施都冇做話唔夠人要佢照番工<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />同埋仲未封院<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T09:22:26.000Z","msg":"[正視聽] 只係停新通行證 一簽多行嘅大陸人係可以照落嚟香港㗎<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1847916\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1847916</a>"},{"pid":"a20c64fb2c8aac2621b15429797c9c820f964308","tid":1847053,"uid":149181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3f457ffdba9f062d178a3a355762e33634b004b1","tid":1847053,"uid":13387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T09:21:42.000Z","msg":"柒婆都係唔肯封福田 羅湖口岸<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔罷工一齊中肺炎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T12:34:15.000Z","msg":"罷佢老母"}]}